data.description: GREAT LOCATION! This 3 bed, 2 full/1 half bath gem boasts over 2000 finished feet of space, 2 living rooms, wood-burning fireplace, Andersen Windows, main floor laundry, and partially finished basement for extra living space. Outside enjoy the covered front porch swing or large patio on over a 1/2 acre lot. Property features two concrete driveways leading to two garages, a detached 36x24 pole building (finished with drywall, natural gas heat, and electric) and a 2-car attached garage. Proximity to the Coldwater Golf Course, North Chain of Lakes, Interstate I-69, and town make this a great home in a great location - schedule your visit today!
